<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MEDIAHUB PRO - Enterprise Video Portal</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
        .main-bg {
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientShift 15s ease infinite;
            transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .bg-kino { background-image: linear-gradient(-45deg, #09090b, #111115, #1c1917, #000000); }
        .bg-anime { background-image: linear-gradient(-45deg, #020617, #0f172a, #1e1b4b, #020617); }
        .bg-multik { background-image: linear-gradient(-45deg, #1e1b4b, #2e1065, #0f172a, #1a103c); }
        .bg-favorites { background-image: linear-gradient(-45deg, #1c1917, #292524, #44403c, #000000); }
        .bg-premium-secret { background-image: linear-gradient(-45deg, #1e1b4b, #4c1d95, #701a75, #000000); }
        
        .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
        .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #09090b; }
        .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #27272a; border-radius: 10px; }
        .custom-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #f59e0b; }
        
        .carousel-container::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
        
        .player-touch-zone {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 35%;
            z-index: 20;
        }
        .touch-left { left: 0; }
        .touch-right { right: 0; }
        .touch-center { left: 35%; width: 30%; }

        .theater-mode-active {
            max-width: 100% !important;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 85vh !important;
        }
        .reply-box { border-left: 2px solid #4b5563; margin-left: 1rem; padding-left: 0.75rem; }
        @keyframes marquee { 0% { transform: translateX(100%); } 100% { transform: translateX(-100%); } }
        .marquee-text { animation: marquee 25s linear infinite; }

        .video-spinner {
            border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border-left-color: #f59e0b;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin { 0% { transform: rotate(0deg); } 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-black text-white font-sans antialiased main-bg bg-kino min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between selection:bg-amber-500 selection:text-black">

    <div id="toastContainer" class="fixed top-5 right-5 z-[350] space-y-3 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div id="globalAnnouncementWrapper" class="bg-amber-500 text-black text-xs font-black py-2 overflow-hidden sticky top-0 z-[50] border-b border-amber-600 shadow-md">
        <div class="whitespace-nowrap inline-block marquee-text" id="announcementText">
            MEDIAHUB PRO TIZIMIGA XUSH KELIBSIZ! AKSIYA VA PREMYERALARNI O'TKAZIB YUBORMANG!
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="ageModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-zinc-950/98 z-[200] flex items-center justify-center p-4 backdrop-blur-lg">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 max-w-lg w-full text-center shadow-2xl relative">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <span class="text-amber-500 text-2xl font-black">18+</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-amber-500 tracking-wider mb-2 uppercase">KIRISH RUXSATI VA NIZOMI</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mb-6 leading-relaxed">Platformadagi eksklyuziv, mistik va premium kontentlardan foydalanish uchun quyidagi 3 ta shartni tasdiqlashingiz shart.</p>
            
            <div class="text-left space-y-4 mb-6 bg-zinc-950 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800">
                <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="checkAge" class="w-5 h-5 rounded border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 text-amber-500 focus:ring-amber-500 mt-0.5">
                    <span class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-medium group-hover:text-white transition"><b>1. Yosh chegarasi:</b> Men 18 yoshga to'lganman yoki undan kattaman.</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="checkHealth" class="w-5 h-5 rounded border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 text-amber-500 focus:ring-amber-500 mt-0.5">
                    <span class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-medium group-hover:text-white transition"><b>2. Salomatlik:</b> Ruhiy holatim va asab tizimim mistik hamda triller syujetlarni ko'rishga tayyor.</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="checkTerms" class="w-5 h-5 rounded border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 text-amber-500 focus:ring-amber-500 mt-0.5">
                    <span class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-medium group-hover:text-white transition"><b>3. Mualliflik huquqi:</b> Saytdagi multimedia kontentlarini ruxsatsiz ko'chirmaslikka roziman.</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 mb-4">
                <button onclick="verifyAge()" class="flex-1 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-black font-black py-3 rounded-xl transition text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">Tasdiqlayman</button>
                <button onclick="exitSite()" class="flex-1 bg-zinc-950 hover:bg-zinc-800 text-red-500 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl transition border border-zinc-800 text-xs uppercase">Rad Etish</button>
            </div>
            <div class="text-[11px] font-black tracking-widest text-zinc-500 border-t border-zinc-800/60 pt-3 uppercase">
                © C R E A T O R [ Muallif ] - <span class="text-amber-500">𝙷𝚘𝚜𝚒𝚕𝚋𝚎𝚔</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="mainContent" class="opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-screen">
        <header class="bg-zinc-950/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-zinc-900 sticky top-0 z-40 shadow-xl">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-2 self-start xl:self-auto">
                    <a href="#" onclick="switchTab('kino')" class="flex items-center text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter group">
                        <span class="text-white pr-1">Media</span>
                        <span class="bg-amber-500 text-black px-2.5 py-1 rounded-xl font-black">hub</span>
                    </a>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-black bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-zinc-400 tracking-wider self-start sm:self-auto uppercase">© 𝙷𝚘𝚜𝚒𝚕𝚋𝚎𝚔</span>
                </div>
                
                <nav class="flex bg-zinc-900 p-1 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 w-full xl:w-[650px] justify-between items-center overflow-x-auto custom-scroll">
                    <button onclick="switchTab('kino')" id="tab-kino" class="flex-1 text-center py-2.5 px-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm font-black bg-amber-500 text-black transition duration-300 min-w-[100px]">KINOLAR</button>
                    <button onclick="switchTab('anime')" id="tab-anime" class="flex-1 text-center py-2.5 px-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm font-black text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300 min-w-[100px]">ANIMELER</button>
                    <button onclick="switchTab('multik')" id="tab-multik" class="flex-1 text-center py-2.5 px-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm font-black text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition duration-300 min-w-[100px]">MULTIKLAR</button>
                    <button onclick="switchTab('favorites')" id="tab-favorites" class="flex-1 text-center py-2.5 px-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm font-black text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 transition duration-300 min-w-[110px]">❤️ SEVIMLILAR</button>
                </nav>
                
                <div class="relative inline-block text-left w-full xl:w-auto">
                    <button onclick="toggleStatsDropdown()" class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs w-full justify-between sm:justify-start hover:border-amber-500 transition">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                            <span class="text-zinc-400 font-medium">Live: <b id="liveUsersCount" class="text-emerald-400 font-mono">110</b></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l border-zinc-800 h-4 mx-1 hidden sm:block"></div>
                        <span class="text-zinc-300">Statistika 📊 <b id="totalViewsCount" class="text-amber-500 font-mono">0</b></span>
                    </button>
                    
                    <div id="statsDropdown" class="hidden absolute right-0 mt-2 w-56 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 shadow-2xl z-[100] p-3 space-y-2 text-xs">
                        <div class="text-[10px] font-black text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-zinc-800 pb-1">Trafik tahlili</div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400"><span>Bugun (Kunlik):</span><b id="statDaily" class="text-white font-mono">0</b></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400"><span>Shu oy (Oylik):</span><b id="statMonthly" class="text-white font-mono">0</b></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400"><span>Shu yil (Yillik):</span><b id="statYearly" class="text-white font-mono">0</b></div>
                        <div class="border-t border-zinc-800 my-1"></div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between font-bold text-amber-400"><span>Yaratilgandan beri:</span><b id="statTotal" class="font-mono">0</b></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-4 max-w-7xl">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 bg-zinc-900/50 backdrop-blur-md p-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800/80 shadow-2xl">
                <a href="https://t.me/MediaHub_Uz_bot" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-sky-500 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-sky-600 text-white font-black py-3 px-4 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition duration-300 shadow-lg">
                    <span>🤖 Bizning Telegram Botimiz</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://t.me/Activist_Uz" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-amber-500 text-amber-400 font-black py-3 px-4 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition duration-300 shadow-lg">
                    <span>👨‍💻 Admin Bilan Bog'lanish</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://instagram.com/_activistuz_" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 via-pink-600 to-yellow-500 hover:opacity-90 text-white font-black py-3 px-4 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider transition duration-300 shadow-lg">
                    <span>📸 Instagram Profilimiz</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="globalAdBannerWrapper" class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-4 max-w-7xl">
            <div id="adBannerClickNode" onclick="triggerAdRedirect()" class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden p-1 flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer hover:border-amber-500 transition duration-300 group shadow-xl">
                <img id="adBannerImage" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618005182384-a83a8bd57fbe?q=80&w=1200" class="w-full h-24 object-cover rounded-xl group-hover:scale-[1.01] transition duration-700" alt="Banner AD">
            </div>
        </div>

        <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6 max-w-7xl flex-grow">
            <div class="mb-8 bg-zinc-950/40 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 shadow-2xl">
                <input type="text" id="searchInput" oninput="searchMovies()" placeholder="Kino nomi, unikal kodi yoki maxfiy kalit so'zni kiriting..." class="flex-grow bg-zinc-900/95 border border-zinc-800 focus:border-amber-500 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white focus:outline-none placeholder-zinc-500 transition shadow-inner">
                <select id="filterYear" onchange="searchMovies()" class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-400 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-xs focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-500 cursor-pointer font-bold">
                    <option value="all">Barcha yillar</option>
                    <option value="2026">2026-yil</option>
                    <option value="2025">2025-yil</option>
                    <option value="2024">2024-yil</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div id="carouselWrapper" class="mb-8 bg-zinc-950/40 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-900/60 shadow-xl relative">
                <h2 class="text-xs font-black tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🔥 PREMYERA VA REYTINGI BALAND KONTENTLAR</h2>
                <div id="carouselContainer" class="carousel-container flex gap-4 overflow-x-auto pb-2 custom-scroll"></div>
            </div>

            <h2 id="categoryTitle" class="text-base sm:text-lg font-black tracking-wider text-amber-500 uppercase border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-3 mb-6">🎬 Dahshatli va Detektiv Kinolar</h2>
            
            <div id="moviesGrid" class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-5"></div>
        </main>

        <footer class="bg-zinc-950 border-t border-zinc-900 py-6 text-center space-y-2">
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-black tracking-widest uppercase">© C R E A T O R [ Muallif ] - <span class="text-amber-500">𝙷𝚘𝚜𝚒𝚕𝚋𝚎𝚔</span></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-600 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">&copy; 2026 MEDIAHUB ENTERPRISE. Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <div id="forcedAdModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/99 z-[400] hidden items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-3xl p-6 max-w-xl w-full space-y-4 text-center">
            <span class="bg-amber-500 text-black font-black text-[9px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider">Homiylik Reklamasi</span>
            <h4 class="text-md font-black uppercase text-white tracking-wide">Videoni ko'rish uchun reklamani tomosha qiling</h4>
            <div class="aspect-video bg-black rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative border border-zinc-800">
                <video id="forcedAdVideoComponent" class="w-full h-full object-contain" playsinline></video>
                <img id="forcedAdImageComponent" class="w-full h-full object-cover hidden" alt="Forced AD Image">
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-950 p-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800">
                <span class="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-medium" id="adTimerFeedback">Reklama tugashiga: 15 soniya qoldi</span>
                <button id="skipAdActionButton" disabled onclick="skipForcedAdAction()" class="bg-zinc-800 text-zinc-500 text-xs font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-xl uppercase transition cursor-not-allowed">O'tkazib yuborish</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="detailsModal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/98 z-[250] hidden items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-4 backdrop-blur-md overflow-y-auto custom-scroll">
        <div id="modalLayoutContainer" class="bg-zinc-950 rounded-3xl max-w-5xl w-full overflow-hidden border border-zinc-800 shadow-2xl flex flex-col transition-all duration-500 my-auto">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-4 border-b border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-900/50">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <h3 id="modalTitle" class="text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide"></h3>
                    <span id="continueWatchingBadge" class="hidden bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 text-emerald-400 text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-mono">Tarix mavjud</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-black border border-zinc-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-400 uppercase">© 𝙷𝚘𝚜𝚒𝚕🇧🇪𝚔</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <button id="toggleTheaterBtn" onclick="toggleTheaterMode()" class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-amber-400 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 hidden">🎭 Teatr Rejimi</button>
                    <button onclick="closeDetailsModal()" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white text-3xl font-light px-2">&times;</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
                <div class="w-full lg:w-3/5 bg-zinc-900 relative aspect-video bg-black flex items-center justify-center" id="modalMediaContainer">
                    <img id="modalPosterImg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="" alt="Poster">
                    
                    <div id="videoPlayerWrapper" class="hidden w-full h-full bg-black relative flex flex-col justify-between group overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="player-touch-zone touch-left" id="playerZoneLeft"></div>
                        <div class="player-touch-zone touch-center" id="playerZoneCenter"></div>
                        <div class="player-touch-zone touch-right" id="playerZoneRight"></div>
                        
                        <div id="playerBufferingLoader" class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/60 z-30 hidden">
                            <div class="video-spinner"></div>
                        </div>

                        <div id="gestureFeedback" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-sm z-50 pointer-events-none opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200"></div>

                        <video id="mainVideoPlayer" class="w-full h-full object-contain z-0" playsinline></video>

                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/80 to-transparent p-3 z-30 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 space-y-2">
                            <input type="range" id="playerProgressBar" min="0" max="100" value="0" step="0.1" oninput="seekVideo(this.value)" class="w-full accent-amber-500 bg-zinc-800 h-1 rounded cursor-pointer">
                            
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <button onclick="togglePlayPause()" id="customPlayBtn" class="bg-amber-500 text-black px-3 py-1 rounded font-black text-[10px] uppercase">PLAY</button>
                                    <span class="text-zinc-400 font-mono text-[11px]" id="playerTimeDisplay">00:00 / 00:00</span>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <button onclick="toggleFullScreen()" class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-300 font-bold uppercase hover:text-white">🖥️ Fullscreen</button>
                                    <select id="playerSpeedSelector" onchange="changePlayerSpeed(this.value)" class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-300 focus:outline-none">
                                        <option value="1.0" selected>Tezlik: 1.0x</option>
                                        <option value="0.5">0.5x</option>
                                        <option value="1.25">1.25x</option>
                                        <option value="1.5">1.5x</option>
                                        <option value="2.0">2.0x</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <select id="playerQualitySelector" onchange="simulateQualitySwitch(this.value)" class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] text-zinc-300 focus:outline-none">
                                        <option value="1080p" selected>Sifat: 1080p HD</option>
                                        <option value="720p">720p Auto</option>
                                        <option value="480p">480p SD</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="modalCodeBadge" class="absolute top-3 left-3 bg-amber-500 text-black text-[10px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md z-20"></div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="w-full lg:w-2/5 p-4 sm:p-6 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-4 bg-zinc-950 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-zinc-900">
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                            <span id="modalGenre" class="text-xs text-amber-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block"></span>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 bg-amber-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 text-xs font-black font-mono">
                                ⭐ <span id="computedRatingValue">0.0</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p id="modalDesc" class="text-zinc-400 text-xs leading-relaxed max-h-[100px] overflow-y-auto custom-scroll pr-1"></p>
                        
                        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 p-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 space-y-2">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs">
                                <button onclick="castVote('like')" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-emerald-500/10 hover:bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/20 transition font-bold">👍 <span id="voteLikeCount">0</span></button>
                                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-400 font-bold" id="voteRatioText">Ratio: 0% / 0%</span>
                                <button onclick="castVote('dislike')" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-red-500/10 hover:bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-red-500/20 transition font-bold">👎 <span id="voteDislikeCount">0</span></button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-zinc-950 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden flex">
                                <div id="voteRatioProgress" class="bg-emerald-500 h-full transition-all duration-500" style="width: 50%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border-t border-zinc-900 pt-3 space-y-2">
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-zinc-500 tracking-wider uppercase block">Foydalanuvchilar sharhi va bahosi</span>
                        <div id="reviewsContainer" class="space-y-2 max-h-[160px] overflow-y-auto custom-scroll pr-1 text-[11px]"></div>
                        
                        <div id="commentFormWrapper" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1.5 pt-2 bg-zinc-900/40 p-2 rounded-xl border border-zinc-900 relative">
                            <div id="replyBadge" class="hidden bg-zinc-900 px-2 py-1 text-[10px] text-amber-400 rounded flex justify-between items-center">
                                <span id="replyBadgeText">Javob berish rejimi...</span>
                                <button onclick="cancelReplyMode()" class="text-red-500 font-bold font-mono">&times;</button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-2">
                                <input type="text" id="reviewerName" placeholder="Ismingiz" class="w-1/2 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-1.5 text-white focus:outline-none text-[11px]">
